<title>March 1996 Washington Watch Newsletter</title>

<body>

<center>
<img src="/townhall/FRC/wwatch/wwatch.gif">
</center>

<p>

Volume 7<br>
Number 5<br>
March 26, 1996

<p><hr width=60% size=3><p>

<center>
