<title>February 1996 Washington Watch Newsletter</title>
<body>
<center><img src="/townhall/FRC/wwatch/wwatch.gif"></center>
<p>
Volume 7<br>
Number 4<br>
January 26, 1996
<p><hr width=60% size=3><p>
<center><h2>CONTENTS</h2></center>
<font size=+1>
