Abstract of the United States 1993, p. 661.
<LI> Conference Report 103-734, op. cit., p. 17.
<LI> Ibid, p. 10.
<LI> Ibid, p. 9.
<LI> Ibid, p. 8.
</OL>
</FONT>

<p>

